        "gg5gx3fXB00_text": "Finally, something that works",
        "gg8XVwOeRnZ_text": "<p>\"I was quoted $9,000 for a neck lift. Decided to try this first because of the guarantee. The sagging isn't completely gone, but it's reduced enough that I don't feel like I need surgery anymore. I cancelled the consultation.\"</p>",
        "ggINzfFhoKQ_text": "<p>Luigi M. — Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggPyyMJdTQJ_text": "Don't just take my word for it:",
        "ggboLgxQG_C_text": "<p>Luca V. — Verified Buyer</p>",
        "ggf0wfYi3U6_text": "Wife thought I got work done",
        "gggbLeY31oh_text": "<p>\"I'm 62 and my wife genuinely thought I'd gotten a procedure. I hadn't—just 8 weeks of using this before bed. The change in my neck was significant enough that she noticed before I did. Best $70 I've spent in years.\"</p>",
        "ggi1ZDKHhU0_text": "<p>\"After spending hundreds on beef tallow creams and every 'men's face cream' I saw advertised on Facebook, this is the first thing that actually works. My neck is tighter. My jawline is more defined. What beef tallow promised, Omnis actually delivered.\"</p>",
        "ggk25TS6Skp_text": "Cancelled my neck lift consultation",
        "ggq3hobzfzH_text": "<p>Robert M. — Verified Buyer</p>"
      },
      "type": "gp-section-601076488938193483"
    },
